event NodeUpdated(address indexed nodeAddress, string metadata, uint256 indexed isNew, uint256 lastSeen)
event OwnershipTransferred(address indexed previousOwner, address indexed newOwner)
function getNode(address nodeAddress) view returns ((address nodeAddress, string metadata, uint256 lastSeen))
function getNodeByNumber(uint256 i) view returns ((address nodeAddress, string metadata, uint256 lastSeen))
function getNodes() view returns ((address nodeAddress, string metadata, uint256 lastSeen)[])
function initialize(address owner, bool requiresWhitelist_, address[] initialNodes, string[] initialMetadata)
function nodes(address) view returns ((address nodeAddress, string metadata, uint256 lastSeen) node, address next, address prev)
function upgradeToAndCall(address newImplementation, bytes data) payable
